 Procurement and Transplantation Network"}, "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Section 372(b) of the\n\t\t\t Public Health Service Act (", "external-xref": {"#tail": ") is amended\u2014", "@parsable-cite": "usc/42/274", "#text": "42 U.S.C. 274(b)", "@legal-doc": "usc"}}, "#text": "\n          ", "subparagraph": [{"#tail": "\n          ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t", "quote": {"#tail": "; and", "#text": ", including standards for preventing the acquisition\n\t\t\t of organs that are infected with the etiologic agent for acquired immune\n\t\t\t deficiency syndrome"}, "#text": "in paragraph\n\t\t\t (2)(E), by striking "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n            ", "#text": "(A)"}, "@id": "H74337C60B19E4AE292FEA7820EFBD245", "#text": "\n            "}, {"#tail": "\n        ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "by adding at the\n\t\t\t end the following:"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n            ", "#text": "(B)"}, "quoted-block": {"@style": "OLC", "@committee-id": "SSHR00", "@changed": "deleted", "after-quoted-block": {"#tail": "\n            ", "#text": "."}, "#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t", "@reported-display-style": "strikethrough", "paragraph": {"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "In adopting and using standards of quality\n\t\t\t\tunder paragraph (2)(E), the Organ Procurement and Transplantation Network may\n\t\t\t\tadopt and use such standards with respect to organs infected with human\n\t\t\t\timmunodeficiency virus (HIV), provided that any such standards ensure that\n\t\t\t\torgans infected with human immunodeficiency virus may be transplanted only into\n\t\t\t\tindividuals who are infected with such virus before receiving such\n\t\t\t\torgan.", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(3)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "Clarification"}, "#text": "\n                ", "@id": "H0F06D64F70CE4F6FA01DE50CBE9A461B"}, "@display-inline": "no-display-inline", "#text": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "@id": "H19B4B65697C04492AE0A033F46D60CEF"}, "#text": "\n            ", "@id": "H85168DAE88714625B6F9AD6EA12660AF"}]}, {"#tail": "\n      ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t", "quote": [{"#tail": " and inserting ", "#text": "including\n\t\t\t arranging for testing with respect to preventing the acquisition of organs that\n\t\t\t are infected with the etiologic agent for acquired immune deficiency\n\t\t\t syndrome"}, {"#tail": ".", "#text": "including arranging for testing with\n\t\t\t respect to identifying organs that are infected with human immunodeficiency\n\t\t\t virus (HIV)"}], "#text": "Section\n\t\t\t 371(b)(3)(C) of the Public Health Service Act (", "external-xref": {"#tail": "; relating\n\t\t\t to organ procurement organizations) is amended by striking ", "@parsable-cite": "usc/42/273", "#text": "42 U.S.C. 273(b)(3)(C)", "@legal-doc": "usc"}, "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n          ", "#text": "(2)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n          ", "#text": "Conforming\n\t\t\t amendment"}, "#text": "\n          ", "@id": "HE8728F60962C47198E7D11EB310D5C56"}], "#text": "\n        ", "@id": "HDE8E85AEA9E94AFE97DA0147FEFAB97E"}, {"#tail": "\n    ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Part H of title III of the Public Health\n\t\t\t Service Act (", "external-xref": {"#tail": ") is amended by inserting after section 377D\n\t\t\t the following:", "@parsable-cite": "usc/42/273", "#text": "42 U.S.C. 273 et seq.", "@legal-doc": "usc"}}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "(b)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "Publication of\n\t\t\t research guidelines"}, "quoted-block": {"@style": "OLC", "@committee-id": "SSHR00", "@changed": "deleted", "after-quoted-block": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "."}, "#tail": "\n\t\t\t", "section": {"#tail": "\n          ", "enum": {"#tail": "\n            ", "#text": "377E."}, "header": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Guidelines,\n\t\t\t\tstandards, and regulations with respect to organs infected with HIV"}, "subsection": [{"#tail": "\n            ", "text": {"short-title": {"#tail": ", the Secretary shall develop and publish guidelines for the\n\t\t\t\tconduct of research relating to transplantation of organs from donors infected\n\t\t\t\twith human immunodeficiency virus (in this section referred to as\n\t\t\t\t", "#text": "HIV Organ Policy Equity\n\t\t\t\tAct"}, "quote": {"#tail": ").", "#text": "HIV"}, "#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Not later than 1 year after the date of the enactment of\n\t\t\t\tthe "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "(a)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "In\n\t\t\t\tgeneral"}, "#text": "\n              ", "@id": "H80A27702459148A09A7A55CF000F4925"}, {"#tail": "\n            ", "text": {"short-title": {"#tail": ", to\n\t\t\t\tthe extent determined by the Secretary to be necessary to allow the conduct of\n\t\t\t\tresearch in accordance with the guidelines developed under subsection\n\t\t\t\t(a)\u2014", "#text": "HIV Organ Policy Equity Act"}, "#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Not\n\t\t\t\tlater than 1 year after the date of the enactment of the\n\t\t\t\t"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "(b)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "Corresponding\n\t\t\t\tchanges to standards and regulations applicable to research"}, "paragraph": [{"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "the Organ\n\t\t\t\tProcurement and Transplantation Network shall revise the standards of quality\n\t\t\t\tadopted under section 372(b)(2)(E); and"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(1)"}, "@id": "H727D1A23DE0F459584BF41659A91D5A2", "#text": "\n                "}, {"#tail": "\n            ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "the Secretary\n\t\t\t\tshall revise ", "external-xref": {"#tail": " of title 42, Code of Federal Regulations (or any\n\t\t\t\tsuccessor regulations).", "@parsable-cite": "cfr/42/121.6", "#text": "section 121.6", "@legal-doc": "regulation"}}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(2)"}, "@id": "H84535491F05F43E4A25183612094AA42", "#text": "\n                "}], "#text": "\n              ", "@id": "H98E5EE8BBE10493D8EB6411DFA25F834"}, {"#tail": "\n          ", "text": {"short-title": {"#tail": ", and annually thereafter, the Secretary,\n\t\t\t\tshall\u2014", "#text": "HIV Organ\n\t\t\t\tPolicy Equity Act"}, "#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Not later than 2 years after\n\t\t\t\tthe date of the enactment of the "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "(c)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "Revision of\n\t\t\t\tstandards and regulations generally"}, "paragraph": [{"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "review the results\n\t\t\t\tof scientific research in conjunction with the Organ Procurement and\n\t\t\t\tTransplantation Network to determine whether the results warrant revision of\n\t\t\t\tthe standards of quality adopted under section 372(b)(2)(E) with respect to\n\t\t\t\tdonated organs infected with HIV and with respect to the safety of cross-strain\n\t\t\t\ttransplantation;"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(1)"}, "@id": "H1E579D5F2C2F4510B3D90914A65151BE", "#text": "\n                "}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "if the Secretary\n\t\t\t\tdetermines under paragraph (1) that such results warrant revision of the\n\t\t\t\tstandards of quality adopted under section 372(b)(2)(E) with respect to donated\n\t\t\t\torgans infected with HIV and with respect to cross-strain transplantation,\n\t\t\t\tdirect the Organ Procurement and Transplantation Network to revise such\n\t\t\t\tstandards, consistent with section 372 and in a way that ensures the changes\n\t\t\t\twill not reduce the safety of organ transplantation; and"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(2)"}, "@id": "HB4D98B2B9E024982BFD4A7504DBAF3A6", "#text": "\n                "}, {"#tail": "\n            ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "in conjunction\n\t\t\t\twith any revision of such standards under paragraph (2), shall revise section\n\t\t\t\t121.6 of title 42, Code of Federal Regulations (or any successor regulations)\n\t\t\t\tfor consistency with such\n\t\t\t\tstandards."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(3)"}, "@id": "H2DB56A2F98F9406E8CE4C28E3A306455", "#text": "\n                "}], "#text": "\n              ", "@id": "H08362A3B82A844E4A693904124569487"}], "#text": "\n            ", "@id": "H42524A5C8F734BF2B1843F2C1F62E714"}, "@reported-display-style": "strikethrough", "@display-inline": "no-display-inline", "#text": "\n\t\t\t\t\t", "@id": "H3B7779335AE64558B894BDBA1F53C565"}, "#text": "\n        ", "@id": "H523D36315ABB42DE85D9B26174DF6D8F"}], "@reported-display-style": "strikethrough", "#text": "\n      ", "@id": "H0C51606D2E964D1CB4DDD4D67D3F550F"}, {"@committee-id": "SSHR00", "@changed": "deleted", "#tail": "\n  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t", "#text": "\n        ", "external-xref": {"#tail": " of title 18, United States\n\t\t\t Code, is amended by adding at the end the following:", "@parsable-cite": "usc/18/1122", "#text": "Section 1122", "@legal-doc": "usc"}, "@display-inline": "no-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n      ", "#text": "3."}, "header": {"#tail": "\n      ", "#text": "Conforming\n\t\t\t amendment to title 18 of the United States Code"}, "quoted-block": {"@style": "USC", "@committee-id": "SSHR00", "@changed": "deleted", "after-quoted-block": {"#tail": "\n      ", "#text": "."}, "#tail": "\n\t\t", "@reported-display-style": "strikethrough", "subsection": {"#tail": "\n        ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t", "#text": "An organ donation does not violate this\n\t\t\t\tsection if the donation is in accordance with all applicable guidelines and\n\t\t\t\tregulations of the Secretary made under section 377E